      "description": "Offered here is a truly pristine, collector-grade vehicle that has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior displays a deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely no rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks, while the wheels are free of any curb rash. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition\u2014smoke-free, with supple leather, crisp electronics, and original floor mats that show zero wear. Mechanically, this car is flawless; it features a full documented service history, a leak-free engine bay, and a smooth, responsive drive that feels brand new. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, operates perfectly. This sale includes all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and a clean title. This is a rare chance to own a 'time capsule' example for the discerning enthusiast.",
